Shared Server Management
========================

Shared Server Management is a simple interface for users on a shared server to
manage their own services.


Installation
------------

git clone git://github.com/m13253/shared-server-management.git
cd shared-server-management
sudo make install


Configuration
-------------

For an example configuration, see ./home/example/rc.d in this repository.


